These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
House: ranch-style, cottage, farmhouse, cape-cod, futuristic
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, daffodil, azalea, begonia
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person who growstulip is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the cape-cod house##1
 6. the cottage house is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 8. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the cottage house##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person who growsdaisy##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| House   | cottage  | ranch-style | farmhouse | cape-cod | futuristic  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Flower         | daffodil | azalea    | tulip | daisy  | begonia |

