.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: pop, dubstep, r&b, trance, blues
The people have 5 different jobs:  accountant, architect, dressmaker, photographer, scientist
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, motorbike, helicopter, scooter
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the photographer is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person driving the boat##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the dressmaker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 8. the fan of r&b is the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the russian is the fan of r&b##1
10. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1
11. the fan of trance is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the fan of r&b is the architect##1
13. the fan of blues is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Music-Genre          | r&b        | blues | dubstep     | trance      | pop  |
| Job           | architect   | dressmaker | scientist    | photographer | accountant |
| Transport   | motorbike | helicopter     | scooter | snowmobile    | boat  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

