.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, mouse, goat, horse
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, dannemann, prince, dunhill, havana
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, scooter, snowmobile, train
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is in the middle##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the prince-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 9. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the prince-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
13. the owner of the goat is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Pet      | goat          | mouse  | ferret       | fish     | horse      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Cigar   | dannemann        | havana | siglo | dunhill    | prince   |
| Transport     | helicopter   | scooter | train      | quad-bike | snowmobile |

