The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, sunflower, iris, rose, amaryllis
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, ferret, fish, rabbit, horse
 1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person who growsbegonia is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the person who growsiris##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific | horror | drama   | superhero |
