 2. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far right##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the fan of gospel is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
10. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
11. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's hobby is writing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks  | writing  | drawing    | gardening | rock-climbing |
