10. the person who likes blue is the owner of the fish##1
11. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of folk##1
12. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
13. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
14. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

