.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
5 different games are played: domino, canasta, whist, scrabble, billiard
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, romance, scientific, western
There are 5 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian, turkish, japanese, mexican
5 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the mexican##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the pakistani##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the egyptian##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the japanese##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Game      | domino      | canasta       | billiard         | scrabble  | whist |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| Nationality   | japanese    | egyptian    | pakistani        | mexican | turkish     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

