.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, ranch-style, futuristic, cottage
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, gospel, jazz
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, baccarat, davidoff, pall-mall, aristoff
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the gothic-revival house is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the ranch-style house is the fan of country##1
 9. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
10. the cain-smoker is the fan of jazz##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the cottage house is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
13. the futuristic house is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| House   | gothic-revival      | futuristic | ranch-style  | cottage    | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | jazz     | country | blues      | folk      |
| Cigar           | davidoff       | cain     | baccarat     | aristoff     | pall-mall   |
| Sport         | basketball | swimming | rowing  | volleyball | sailing   |

