.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, may, december, march, september
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, indie, rock, techno, trance
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, iris, azalea, begonia
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller, ship, tram
 1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the fan of rock is the person who's birthday is in september##1
13. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Birthday      | december | september    | may   | march   | january |
| Music-Genre   | blues    | rock   | trance | techno | indie  |
| Flower           | orchid     | azalea | iris   | begonia | lily   |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | tram   | car    | ship   | roller |

