.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, fantasy, horror, comedy
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, pop, punk, salsa
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, british, italian, polish, thai
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, singing, board-games, camping, baking
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the thai##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the fan of pop is the british##1
 8. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person watching horror movies##1
14. the polish is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre      | disaster | horror   | fantasy    | zombie       | comedy |
| Music-Genre   | pop           | country   | salsa   | punk       | blues  |
| Nationality   | british       | argentine | italian | polish     | thai   |
| Hobby     | board-games    | singing   | camping   | cooking | baking   |

 